"║                                                                       ║\n"
"║ To adjust the emulated CPU speed, press [color=light-red]%s+F11[color=white] and [color=light-red]%s+F12[color=white].%s%s        ║\n"
"║ To open the keymapper, press [color=light-red]%s+F1[color=white].%s                                 ║\n"
